data.description: Welcome to this Beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 full Bath Renovated Ranch on 6.5 Acres Featuring all Brand new 3-pane windows throughout the home. Doors and Sliding glass Patio Door all brand new and installed in 2024. Cozy up to the brand-new fireplace in the large family room and watch your favorite movie. 30x24 attached garage built in 2022, Newly Fenced in back yard and a crushed asphalt driveway. What more could you ask for?
